subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal, a two-time Wimbledon champion, could face top-seeded Novak Djokovic, Andy Murray, Roger Federer or David Ferrer as early as the quarterfinals.
